snippet.title: Guaranteed solvable algorithm playing classic mode
snippet.description:
Little demo of the guaranteed solving algorithm.

Colour code: 
Blue - Tile being evaluated
Green - Tile queued to be evaluated
Orange - Tile unsolvable for now and skipped in queue
White - Tile solved
Flag - Mine flagged
Dark Grey - Unknown tile
Red/Yellow - Mine swapped from red to yellow (doesn't happen here)

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/982220/Globesweeper/
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.IncandescentGames.Globesweeper
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/globesweeper/id1439036627
